An introduction to networking, you can learn how computer networks work, the architecture used to design networks and how to keep them safe. A computer network enables communication for every business, entertainment and research purpose. The internet, online search, email, audio and video sharing, online commerce, live-streaming, all social networking exist because of computer networking. There are different kinds of networking, LAN and WAN. LAN networking is a local area networking and connects computers in a defined physical space, and WAN is a wide area network that connects computers across continents, connecting billions of computers worldwide. Some important terms and concepts are IP addresses, Nodes, Routers, Switches, Ports, and Network cable types are all great terms for understanding the networking of computers. 
